        username as ""
        password as ""
        timeout as driver.config.timeout as integer
        retry_attempts as 3
        ssl_enabled as false
        ssl_verify as false
        connection_string as driver.database_path
        driver_options as driver.config as dictionary

Process called "get_pool_config_from_driver" that takes driver as SQLiteDriver returns connection_pool.PoolConfiguration:
