        Note: For demonstration, return mock data based on query type
        Let query be cursor["last_query"] as String
        If starts_with with text as query and prefix as "SELECT":
            Note: Return sample data for SELECT queries
            Return list containing Dictionary with:
                "id" as 1
                "name" as "Sample Record"
                "created_at" as datetime.now as string
        
        Return empty list
    
    Catch error as Exception:
