        Let query be cursor["last_query"] as String
        If starts_with with text as query and prefix as "INSERT":
            Note: This would call sqlite3_last_insert_rowid()
            Return 1  Note: Simulate insert ID
        
        Return none
    
    Catch error as Exception:
        Return none

Process called "get_sqlite_total_changes" that takes cursor as Any returns Integer:
